18/11/2003
ANKARA, Turkey -- US State Department Special Envoy for Cyprus Thomas Weston arrived in Turkey on Monday (17 November) to discuss possible solutions to the Cyprus dispute. After arriving, he said the only chance for a solution was to use the UN-proposed reunification plan as a basis for negotiation. He also stressed the urgency involved, given Cyprus' upcoming accession to the EU. (Anadolu Agency, NTV - 17/11/03)
